data.description: Arcadia Lite condominium is in an ideal location close to all the great restaurants and nightlife in the area. 10 minutes to the airport, this gated, owner occupied 2 bedroom home is nice for full or part time occupants. Large community pool and spa area is a close walk away. Two full bathrooms. Main bedroom has a balcony off it to enjoy quiet time. Come and see and be your own landlord!
